Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:22.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}你心中潛伏的PRISONER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:24.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}背負永不消失的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:29.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}為必須守護的世界 請別嘆息
